   ===========
   DESCRIPTION
   ===========
   WebMarkupMin.WebForms contains 3 Web Forms page classes: CompressedPage
   (only supports GZIP/Deflate compression), MinifiedAndCompressedHtmlPage
   (supports HTML minification and GZIP/Deflate compression) and
   MinifiedAndCompressedXhtmlPage (supports XHTML minification and
   GZIP/Deflate compression); and 3 master page classes:
   CompressedMasterPage (only supports GZIP/Deflate compression),
   MinifiedAndCompressedHtmlMasterPage (supports HTML minification and
   GZIP/Deflate compression) and MinifiedAndCompressedXhtmlMasterPage
   (supports XHTML minification and GZIP/Deflate compression).
